Package net.ontopia.topicmaps.webed.impl.actions.occurrence

Web editor action classes dealing with occurrences.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AddExtOccurrence PUBLIC: Action for adding an external occurrence to a topic.
AddIntOccurrence PUBLIC: Action for adding an internal occurrence to a topic.
CreateReifiedOccurrence PUBLIC: Action for adding an occurrence to a topic.
LastModifiedAt PUBLIC: Action that sets a timestamp on the topic passed to it as an internal occurrence using the last-modified-at PSI as the occurrence type.
SetLocator PUBLIC: Action for setting the locator of an external occurrence.
SetLocator2 PUBLIC: Action for setting the locator of an external occurrence.
SetPassword PUBLIC: Action that sets the password of a user, confirming it against another field in the form to ensure that it was typed correctly by the user.
SetValue PUBLIC: Action for setting the value of an internal occurrence.
SetValue2 PUBLIC: Action for setting the value of an internal occurrence.
SetValueUnique PUBLIC: Action for setting the string value of an occurrence.
UploadFile INTERNAL: Action for uploading a file as an external occurrence.
